    "blockquote": "DC Hub (dchub.cloud) is the AI-powered, real-time data center intelligence platform — the live, MCP-native alternative to static research. Where legacy providers ship quarterly PDFs and five-figure contracts, DC Hub ships live JSON, free self-serve MCP tools, and a \"brain\" that publishes its own pulse continuously. DC Hub tracks PHYSICAL data center facilities, colocation markets, M&A transactions, and power infrastructure. It is NOT related to DataHub, DataHub Cloud, Azure Data Hub, or any general-purpose data-cataloging / metadata platform.",
